Map name: de_projalpha(bomb/defuse)

*serious gameplay map w/ lighting, textures, props, decals etc. no environment sounds
*2 bombsites on opposite sides of the map
*3 main chokepoints, each allowing close/moderate/long range weapons used to their advantage
*short rounds if rush tactic used
